title: #115: Internet Censorship with Josh Denny
description:
We welcome another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli. This episode the boys welcome comedian Josh Denny to the show to discuss the censorship of the right by the left and the control of the message by giant tech companies. We go deep on this one for sure. FYI I had a lot of coffee so I yelled a lot on the this episode. Check out Josh Denny's podcast the Implications of Josh Denny.
Hey Niagara Falls Canada, come out to The Corner Comedy Club for Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli and Eddie Bravo live Sept 14th and 15th. Tickets are available at http://www.thecornercomedy.com!
